CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.sdoh_hud_pit_homelessness.hud_pit_by_coc`
(

  CoC_Name STRING OPTIONS(description="Name of the Continuum of Care Area"),
  CoC_Category STRING OPTIONS(description="Only for 2018"),
  Overall_Homeless INT64 OPTIONS(description="Total Homeless Population"),
  Sheltered_ES_Homeless INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homeless in Emergency Shelters"),
  Sheltered_TH_Homeless INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homeless in Transitional Housing"),
  Sheltered_SH_Homeless INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homeless in Safe Haven Housing"),
  Sheltered_Total_Homeless INT64 OPTIONS(description="Total Sheltered Homeless"),

  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_Individuals INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing"),
  Sheltered_SH_Homeless_Individuals INT64 OPTIONS(description="Safe Haven Housing"),
  Sheltered_Total_Homeless_Individuals INT64,
  Unsheltered_Homeless_Individuals INT64,
  Homeless_People_in_Families INT64,

  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_People_in_Families INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing"),

  Sheltered_Total_Homeless_Family_Households INT64,
  Unsheltered_Homeless_Family_Households INT64,

  Sheltered_SH_Chronically_Homeless INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homelessness for a Year"),
  Sheltered_Total_Chronically_Homeless INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homelessness for a Year"),
  Unsheltered_Chronically_Homeless INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homelessness for a Year"),
  Chronically_Homeless_Individuals INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homelessness for a Year"),
  Sheltered_ES_Chronically_Homeless_Individuals INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; Homelessness for a Year"),
  Sheltered_SH_Chronically_Homeless_Individuals INT64 OPTIONS(description="Safe Haven Housing; Homelessness for a Year"),
  Sheltered_Total_Chronically_Homeless_Individuals INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homelessness for a Year"),
  Unsheltered_Chronically_Homeless_Individuals INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homelessness for a Year"),
  Chronically_Homeless_People_in_Families INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homelessness for a Year"),
  Sheltered_ES_Chronically_Homeless_People_in_Families INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; Homelessness for a Year"),
  Sheltered_Total_Chronically_Homeless_People_in_Families INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homelessness for a Year"),
  Unsheltered_Chronically_Homeless_People_in_Families INT64 OPTIONS(description="Homelessness for a Year"),
  Homeless_Veterans INT64,
  Sheltered_ES_Homeless_Veterans INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; after 2013"),
  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_Veterans INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing; after 2013"),
  Sheltered_SH_Homeless_Veterans INT64 OPTIONS(description="Safe Haven Housing; after 2013"),
  Sheltered_Total_Homeless_Veterans INT64,
  Unsheltered_Homeless_Veterans INT64,
  Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Sheltered_ES_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_SH_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Safe Haven Housing; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_Total_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Unsheltered_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Sheltered_ES_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_SH_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Safe Haven Housing; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_Total_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Unsheltered_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Sheltered_ES_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_SH_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Safe Haven Housing; after 2014"),

  Unsheltered_Homeless_Unaccompanied_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Sheltered_ES_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_Total_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Unsheltered_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_25 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Sheltered_ES_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_Total_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Unsheltered_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Under_18 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Sheltered_ES_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_Total_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Unsheltered_Homeless_Parenting_Youth_Age_18_24 INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Homeless_Children_of_Parenting_Youth INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Sheltered_ES_Homeless_Children_of_Parenting_Youth INT64 OPTIONS(description="Emergency Shelter; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_TH_Homeless_Children_of_Parenting_Youth INT64 OPTIONS(description="Transitional Housing; after 2014"),
  Sheltered_Total_Homeless_Children_of_Parenting_Youth INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),
  Unsheltered_Homeless_Children_of_Parenting_Youth INT64 OPTIONS(description="after 2014"),

OPTIONS(
  description="Methodology: https://files.hudexchange.info/resources/documents/PIT-Count-Methodology-Guide.pdf; this table combines count information from 2012 through 2018",
  labels=[("freebqcovid", "")]
);
